Create a .env file in the root of your project and add the following environment variables:
```
# Database configuration
DATABASE_URL="your_database_url"
DIRECT_URL="your_direct_url"
# Supabase public keys (for client-side)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL="your_supabase_url"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="your_publishable_key"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="your_anon_key"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_STORAGE_BUCKET="your_storage_bucket"
# Service role (server-side only, NOT public)
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="your_service_role_key"
# PayOS
PAYOS_CLIENT_ID="your_payos_client_id"
PAYOS_API_KEY="your_payos_api_key"
PAYOS_CHECKSUM_KEY="your_payos_checksum_key"
```
Make sure to replace the placeholder values with your actual configuration values from Supabase and PayOS.